menuconfig LIB_SEL4_CXX
    bool "Support library for compiling C++ applications on seL4"
    default y
    help
        This library aims to add missing definitions between the GCC C++ standard library
        and the muslc standard library. Hopefully this allows a regular STL and C++ support
        library to be compiled and linked in, but this whole thing is a hack
